et printouts to our doorsteps now.",date:"Aug 18 2022"}]}},r={title:"How Print Store works",subtitle:"Let Blinkit Print Store take care of your everyday printing needs",steps:[{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/visit_web.png",title:"Visit Print Store",description:"Open Blinkit app and visit Print Store"},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/upload_web.png",title:"Upload file(s)",description:"Upload a file or multiple files to take prints"},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/customise_web.png",title:"Customise print",description:"Choose print settings as per your requirement "},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/checkout_web.png",title:"Checkout",description:"Add prints to cart and place an order"}],customisation:{title:"Customisation options",items:[{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/type_web.png",title:"Upload any file type",description:"Print PDF, JPG, PNG, JPEG, and many more"},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/color_web.png",title:"Black & White / Colour",description:"Save cost with black & white or pick the coloured option "},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/size_web.png",title:"Paper format size",description:"We work only with A4 printing paper of 70 GSM"},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/orientation_web.png",title:"Orientation",description:"Choose landscape or portrait as per your need"}]}},i={title:"Solution for convenient printing needs!",subtitle:"Flexible Printing applications for multiple needs",steps:[{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/needs_paasport.png",subtitle:"Passport, Visa and Travel Documents"},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/needs_aadhar.png",subtitle:"Aadhar card / ID proofs"},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/needs_homework.png",subtitle:"Homework / Class Work / Assignments"},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/needs_activity.png",subtitle:"Activity and Hobby Sheets"},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/needs_Ebook.png",subtitle:"eBooks & Leisure Reading Articles"},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/needs_resume.png",subtitle:"Resumes & Work related documents"},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/needs_bank.png",subtitle:"Bank & Official Govt. Documents"},{image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/needs_invoice.png",subtitle:"Invoices & Bills"}]},n={title:"Blog: Printouts delivered to your doorstep",content:"Ever needed to print out an assignment or boarding pass or even visa application forms at the last minute only to realise that the ink in the printer has turned into a piece of rock. Yes, we relate to the pain as well.\n\t\nIn August 2022, Blinkit launched printing services in select areas of Delhi NCR. The need was very selfish - we all felt that sporadic printing should not be a burden that occupies permanent space in our lives only to fail us when we really need it. It also helped that our existing distribution network enabled us to deliver high quality printouts to our customers at their doorsteps\n\t\nWhy we built this service I have bought three printers...",image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/blog_banner_Web.png",link:"https://blinkit.com/blog/printout"},s=["PDF Print","Annual Report Printing","Fitness Plan Printing","Legal Document Print","Homework Worksheet Printing","Survey & Questionnaire Printing","Script Printing","College Work","School Work","College Work","Assignments","Activity Sheets","Colouring Books","eBooks","Articles and PDFs","Memes","Photographs","ID Proofs","Aadhar Card","Tax fillings","Lease agreement","Tax fillings","Tax proofs","Event Programmes","Newsletter Printing","A4 Printing","Books","Study Material / Guide Printing","School Book Printing","Magazine","School Book Printing","Comic Book Printing","Family History Book Printing","Bulk Book Printing","Gaming Rulebook","Children Book","Portfolios","Year Book","Instructions Print","Instructions Print","Thesis Print","Flyers, Pamphlet or Leaflet - Black and White Printing","Dissertation Print","Final Major Project","Thesis Dissertation Print","Notecards","Certificate Print","Flyers, Pamphlet or Leaflet - Black and White Printing","Letterhead Printing","Bill Books","Notebook","Photo Calendar","Passport forms ","Visa forms","Travel tickets","Bank applications","Religious Printing & Publishing","Training / Instruction Manual Printing","Presentation","Proposal Print","Table and Tentcards","Official documents","Government documents","Bills","Rental agreement","Invoices"];t.keywords=s;var o={title:"Many more needs Print Store could fullfil",tags:s},c=[{title:"About Print Store",image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/print_store_web.png",content:"Blinkit launched printing services in select pin codes across India. The need was very selfish - we felt that sporadic printing should not be a burden that occupies permanent space in our lives and in our houses (for some) only to fail us when we really need it. It also helped that our existing distribution network enabled us to deliver high quality printouts to our customers at their doorsteps."},{title:"About Blinkit",image:"https://cdn.grofers.com/assets/ui/print/bl_logo_web.png",content:"Imagine needing something when you are at home and getting it before you have tied your shoelaces to step out. We are revolutionizing e-commerce by making the stuff most important to you, available to you in a blink of your eye. We want our customers to focus on the more important things for themselves and not need to plan for the little things that life needs on an everyday basis. We are here to get your chores out of your way.\nOur mission is – “instant commerce indistinguishable from magic”. Using a backbone of technology, data sciences, and rich customer",link:"https://blinkit.com/aboutus"}],l={title:"When it comes to printing services, there are two primary options to consider:",points:[{title:"Online printing services"},{title:"Traditional brick-and-mortar printing shops"}],content:[{text:"Online printing services like Blinkit are becoming increasingly popular due to print convenience and competitive pricing. However, traditional printing shops have been around for years and continue to offer a range of printing options."},{text:"When it comes to online printing services, there are several factors to consider. First of all, it's important to choose a service that offers a range of printing options, including document printing, certificate printing, and bulk printing. Additionally, one has to ensure that the service provides high-quality printing and a range of paper options. Blinkit offers all these things at one place."},{text:"One benefit of trying online printing service is the convenience factor. With Blinkit's printing service, one can upload documents from the comfort of their home and have them delivered right to their doorstep. This can save time and energy, especially for businesses and organizations that require frequent printing services."},{text:"Another benefit of using an online printing service is the ability to track printing orders. Many online printing services offer user-friendly websites that allow users to track the status of printing orders and receive notifications when the orders are shipped. This ensure that your printing needs are met in a timely manner."},{text:"Blinkit launched online printing services recently. We differentiate ourselves from other online printing service providers through our delivery time. We provide high quality printing and a range of printing customisation options to choose from. We also offer competitive pricing and instant turn around times, making us a great option for individuals, businesses and organizations in need of printing services."},{text:"Blinkit is a reputable company that offers high quality printing services via its online printing offering. We provide high quality printing and a range of printing customisation options to choose from. We also offer competitive pricing and instant turn around times, making us a great option for individuals, businesses and organizations in need of printing services."},{text:"Another important factor which one should consider when choosing an online printing service is the pricing. One should look for a service that offers competitive pricing and a range of pricing options. Additionally, one should ensure that the service provides transparent pricing, so users can easily understand the cost also."},{text:"Blinkit offers competitive pricing for all type of printing services. We provide transparent pricing on our website, so one can easily understand the cost of their printing order. "},{text:"When it comes to color printing, there are a few factors to consider. Color printing is more expensive than black and white printing, so it's important to choose a service that offers competitive pricing for color prints. Additionally, ensure that the service provides high-quality color printing."},{text:"Blinkit offers high-quality color printing services at competitive prices. We use state-of-the-art printing technology to ensure that one's color printing needs are met with precision and accuracy."},{text:"Overall, online printing services like Blinkit offer a convenient and cost-effective option for individuals, businesses and organisations in need of printing services. By considering factors like quality of service, convenience, and pricing, one can find the best printing option"}]},d=[{type:1e3,grid_span:12,data:a,layout_config:{max_width:1160,margin_top:80,margin_bottom:80}},{type:1001,grid_span:12,data:r,layout_config:{max_width:1160,bg_color:"#E8EAF5",margin_top:80,margin_bottom:80}},{type:1002,grid_span:12,data:n,layout_config:{max_width:1160,bg_color:"#ffffff",margin_top:80,margin_bottom:80}},{type:1003,grid_span:12,data:i,layout_config:{max_width:1160,bg_color:"#E8EAF5",margin_top:80,margin_bottom:80}}];t.seoWidgets=d;var u=[{type:1e3,grid_span:12,data:a,layout_conf